bullshit advice among these pages, which is why we love them. Give one—or all—of them a read. They just might change your life.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_4\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_4\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"db61\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-subtle-art-of-not-giving-a-f-ck\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*OMfwgSz4AZnOEnTlymKJRg.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_5\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_5\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"5e33\",\"text\":\"If you’ve read any of popular blog writer Mark Manson’s content, you know you’re in for a treat with this one. The Subtle Art of Not Giving a F*ck is a truly refreshing take on what it means to live a great life. Manson is a tell-it-like-it-is guy, dropping lines like, “In life, we have a limited amount of fucks to give. So you must choose your fucks wisely.” Still, his writing is genuine and hits you right in the gut—in the best possible way. If you can’t stand traditional self-help books but are still curious about what it means to live a life full of happiness and contentment (who doesn’t?), this is the perfect book for you.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":42,\"end\":53,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fmarkmanson.net\\u002F\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":111,\"end\":146,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-subtle-art-of-not-giving-a-f-ck\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":42,\"end\":55,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":111,\"end\":146,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_6\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_6\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"2213\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fif-you-feel-too-much\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*S6ME3kyP_LwRuVGb8kJrfw.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_7\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_7\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"57f8\",\"text\":\"This is a breathtakingly written memoir from the founder of To Write Love On Her Arms, a non-profit aimed at presenting hope for people who struggle with addiction, depression, self-injury, and thoughts of suicide. Author Jamie Tworkowski touches on achey subjects—from heartbreak to the death of loved ones. This is a soothing, and ultimately a redemptive, read that will make you feel like you’ve got a friend who knows exactly what you were going through during the toughest experiences of your own life.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":33,\"end\":39,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fif-you-feel-too-much\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":60,\"end\":85,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Ftwloha.com\\u002F\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":33,\"end\":39,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":60,\"end\":87,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_8\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_8\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"3d0b\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fdaring-greatly\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*Fmw2pQYw-YV2ZIEI-cWjVA.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_9\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_9\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"3d12\",\"text\":\"It has to be said: Daring Greatly is one of those books that every human on the planet should read. If everyone understood and lived by the concepts that author Brené Brown explores, we’d all be happier and better for it. This book centers around the topic of vulnerability, exploring what it means to live a courageous life in a world where we too often make decisions out of fear that we’ll get hurt or be criticized. This is a powerful book that will change your willingness and practice around letting yourself be fully seen—by loved ones and strangers alike.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":19,\"end\":33,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fdaring-greatly\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":19,\"end\":33,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_10\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_10\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"9763\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Ftiny-beautiful-things\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*sw42Rk9IkrBVZTEC1XlEMQ.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_11\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_11\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"3591\",\"text\":\"This is legitimately one of the most beautifully self-help books you’ll ever read. Author Cheryl Strayed compiles a series of Q&As from her days as an anonymous advice columnist—and boy, will her thoughts blow you away. Tiny Beautiful Things takes readers on a journey through seemingly impossible topics like: navigating divorce, unrequited love, addiction, betrayal, and forgiveness. Her advice feels deeply genuine and honest‚ like you’re getting it from a much smarter, more compassionate big sister. Author Ryan Holiday says, “This book contains some of the most cogent insights on life, pain, loss, love, success, and youth that I have ever seen.” He’s not exaggerating. Go read this one now.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":220,\"end\":241,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Ftiny-beautiful-things\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":220,\"end\":241,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_12\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_12\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"88b4\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fleadership-and-self-deception\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*NEzaoyUXVoPnnxyi7x5rKw.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_13\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_13\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"d3d2\",\"text\":\"Leadership and Self-Deception is the kind of book that will completely change the quality of your relationships—at work and beyond—for the better. Through memorable storytelling, It reads almost like a novel, but it does an incredible job of getting readers to think about how we view others and why that impacts our ability to lead (or even communicate effectively) with them. You’ll walk away from this one with a renewed perspective on what it means to lead well by first changing your own thinking, along with strengthening your ability to relate to and empathize with others. You’ll never look at the critical conversations you have—at work or home—the same way again.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":29,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fleadership-and-self-deception\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":29,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_14\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_14\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"353b\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fmindset-2\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*urpfDN5v3xZ41XskIApfFA.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_15\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_15\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"a08c\",\"text\":\"Mindset is a well-regarded psychology book that explores the power of one’s thinking. Dweck’s core theory is that is isn’t just our talent that makes us successful, but more importantly, whether we approach life with a fixed or growth mindset. With a fixed mindset, you believe failure means something is wrong with you. On the other hand, with a growth mindset, you see failure as an opportunity to grow and become better. The author guides us through various topics—from parenting and relationships, to school and business—and explains how developing a growth mindset in all areas of our lives can help us reach our full potential. This book gets a bit repetitive at some points, but it is most certainly worth the read.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":7,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fmindset-2\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":7,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_16\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_16\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"2aec\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-road-less-traveled\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*jmyBcuERz9jQvfhIQf_blg.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_17\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_17\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"e36b\",\"text\":\"The Road Less Traveled is a truly profound book. The author, M. Scott Peck, opens with the line, “Life is difficult.” This read is the ultimate roadmap to dealing with some of life’s greatest challenges with grace and love. Topics include: how to problem solve; dealing with pain; delaying gratification; being open to challenge; and developing a dedication to reality and personal growth. More than anything, these 315 pages will leave you feeling more in touch with the greatest truths in the universe—and how they can guide you to greater heights of self-understanding and love.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":22,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-road-less-traveled\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":22,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_18\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_18\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"fb6a\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-school-of-greatness-2\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*W5hyzlXi4KB21ekkJnBoOA.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_19\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_19\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"eadf\",\"text\":\"The School of Greatness is an uplifting read by author Lewis Howes (who also hosts an awesome podcast by the same name, which you can check out here). Over the last several years, he’s interviewed hundreds of successful athletes, entrepreneurs, creatives, and thought leaders—from Tony Robbins to Elizabeth Gilbert to Larry King. In this book, he lays out his framework for personal development based on what he’s learned from all of those people that he calls his greatness “professors.” You’ll learn how to clarify your vision, master your body, build positive habits, and live a life of service. This is a great book that will help you find clarity and motivation around your biggest personal goals.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":23,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-school-of-greatness-2\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":144,\"end\":148,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"http:\\u002F\\u002Flewishowes.com\\u002Fcategory\\u002Fpodcast\\u002F\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":0,\"end\":23,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":144,\"end\":148,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_20\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_20\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"6072\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-untethered-soul\",\"layout\":\"INSET_CENTER\",\"metadata\":{\"__ref\":\"ImageMetadata:1*gNllwjuA61ZgBAzJCGrDoQ.png\"},\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_21\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_21\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"2b2b\",\"text\":\"My goodness, The Untethered Soul is the kind of read that will make you want to highlight basically everything. It’s a transformative read that will help you better understand and become aware of the limiting beliefs and (often unconscious) negative thoughts that drive many of the decisions you make (or don’t make) in your life. One of the biggest takeaways is that you are not your thoughts, but rather, the observer of your thoughts. While this concept may seem a bit obscure at first, Singer uses poignant metaphors and parables to explain it in a way that will resonate—and possibly change the way you think about yourself and the world forever. This is a delightfully illuminating book.\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":13,\"end\":32,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fbooks\\u002Fthe-untethered-soul\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":13,\"end\":32,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":376,\"end\":380,\"type\":\"EM\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":411,\"end\":420,\"type\":\"EM\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_22\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_22\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"d13f\",\"text\":\"Looking for more books that just might change your life? Browse through Product Hunt’s book collections and find your next read here:\",\"type\":\"P\",\"href\":null,\"layout\":null,\"metadata\":null,\"hasDropCap\":null,\"iframe\":null,\"mixtapeMetadata\":null,\"markups\":[{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":108,\"end\":132,\"type\":\"A\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fsearch\\u002Fcollections?q=books\",\"anchorType\":\"LINK\",\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null},{\"__typename\":\"Markup\",\"start\":108,\"end\":132,\"type\":\"STRONG\",\"href\":null,\"anchorType\":null,\"userId\":null,\"linkMetadata\":null}],\"dropCapImage\":null},\"Paragraph:1bdf24822843_23\":{\"id\":\"1bdf24822843_23\",\"__typename\":\"Paragraph\",\"name\":\"07dd\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMG\",\"href\":\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fwww.producthunt.com\\u002Fs