ge wp-stateless-item\" alt=\"Kohli last century: When was the last time Virat Kohli had scored an international century?\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-src=\"https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century.jpg 1280w, https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-770x433.jpg 770w, https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-20x11.jpg 20w, https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-385x217.jpg 385w\" data-attachment-id=\"228137\" data-permalink=\"https://thesportsrush.com/cricket-news-kohli-last-century-when-was-the-last-time-virat-kohli-had-scored-an-international-century/kohli-last-century/\" data-orig-file=\"https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1280,720\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kohli last century\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com/2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century-1024x576.jpg\" data-image-size=\"goodlife-post-style1\" data-stateless-media-bucket=\"cdn-wp.thesportsrush.com\" data-stateless-media-name=\"2021/03/866fed8d-kohli-last-century.jpg\" />					  </figure>\n				  <div class=\"share-container\">\n								  <div class=\"post-content-container\">\n										<div class=\"post-content entry-content cf\">\n											<div class=\'code-block code-block-11\' style=\'margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; background: transparent !important;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - sportrush_app - top_of_page -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-170\">\n<script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js\"></script>\n<!-- after content 2020 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\n     style=\"display:block\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"1943969387\"\n     data-ad-format=\"auto\"\n     data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - sportrush_app - top_of_page -->\n</div>\n<div class=\'code-block code-block-2 ai-viewport-3\' style=\'margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;\'>\n<amp-ad width=\"100vw\" height=\"320\"\n     type=\"adsense\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"4587580375\"\n     data-auto-format=\"rspv\"\n     data-full-width=\"\">\n  <div overflow=\"\"></div>\n</amp-ad></div>\n<p><strong>Virat Kohli last century: The Indian captain scored a second consecutive impact-generating half-century at the Narendra Modi Stadium.</strong></p>\n<p>During the third T20I of the ongoing England&#8217;s tour of India in Ahmedabad, India captain Virat Kohli led from the front to rescue his team from a difficult position.</p>\n<p>Kohli, who came out to bat at No. 4 after more than a year, found himself in the middle in the powerplay. In addition to a dearth of runs, India were also struggling due to losing wickets at regular intervals back then which included Kohli and wicket-keeper batsman Rishabh Pant (25) getting involved in a <a href=\"https://thesportsrush.com/cricket-news-terrible-running-fans-react-to-rishabh-pant-run-out-after-miscommunication-with-virat-kohli-vs-england/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">massive miscommunication</a>.</p><div class=\'code-block code-block-25 ai-viewport-3\' style=\'margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - under_first_paragraph 102 - under_first_paragraph -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-102\">\n<amp-ad width=\"100vw\" height=\"320\"\n     type=\"adsense\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"1063042683\"\n     data-auto-format=\"rspv\"\n     data-full-width=\"\">\n  <div overflow=\"\"></div>\n</amp-ad>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - under_first_paragraph 102 - under_first_paragraph -->\n</div>\n<div class=\'code-block code-block-17\' style=\'margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - after_3rd_para - under_first_paragraph -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-141\">\n<script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js\"></script>\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\n     style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\"\n     data-ad-layout=\"in-article\"\n     data-ad-format=\"fluid\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"7314321969\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - after_3rd_para - under_first_paragraph -->\n</div>\n\n<p>Having scored 14* (14) at the halfway mark with India reeling at 55/3, the hosts needed Kohli to bat till the end &#8211; something which he did successfully at the Narendra Modi Stadium.</p><div class=\'code-block code-block-8\' style=\'margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - amp_after_5th_para - longest_content -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-147\">\n<div id = \'vdo_ai_div\'></div><script>(function(v,d,o,ai){ai=d.createElement(\'script\');ai.defer=true;ai.async=true;ai.src=v.location.protocol+o;d.head.appendChild(ai);})(window, document, \'//a.vdo.ai/core/thesportsrush/vdo.ai.js\');</script>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - amp_after_5th_para - longest_content --></div>\n\n<p>It was in the last five overs that Kohli scored 49* (17) to power India to 156/6 in 20 overs. Having started the assault by hitting a four and a six off England spearhead Jofra Archer in the 16th over, Kohli replicated the same against Chris Jordan in the following over.</p><div class=\'code-block code-block-26 ai-viewport-2 ai-viewport-3\' style=\'margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - mid_content 131 - mid_content -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-131\"> \n<amp-ad width=\"100vw\" height=\"320\"\n     type=\"adsense\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"1021769952\"\n     data-auto-format=\"rspv\"\n     data-full-width=\"\">\n  <div overflow=\"\"></div>\n</amp-ad>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - mid_content 131 - mid_content -->\n</div>\n\n<p>England&#8217;s Mark Wood, who had troubled the Indian batsmen with his pace in the powerplay, had no clue against Kohli&#8217;s brilliance as the right-hand batsman played second to none shots to hit two sixes and a four in the 18th over.</p>\n<h4>Virat Kohli last century</h4>\n<p>Top-scoring for his team in the second consecutive match, Kohli scored a valiant 77* (46) which comprised of eight fours and four sixes. In what is Kohli&#8217;s 27th T20I half-century, it is also his second in as many matches.</p><div class=\'code-block code-block-28 ai-track\' data-ai=\'WzI4LDAsIkJsb2NrIDI4IiwiIiwxXQ==\' style=\'margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;\'>\n<div id=\'b-thesportsrush\'></div><script>\n  (function(v, d, o, ai) {\n    ai = d.createElement(\'script\');\n    ai.defer = true;\n    ai.async = true;\n    ai.src = v.location.protocol + o;\n    d.head.appendChild(ai);\n  })(window, document, \'//a.vdo.ai/core/b-thesportsrush/vdo.ai.js\');\n</script></div>\n\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">This has been a masterclass from Virat Kohli. If you&#8217;re a young batsman anywhere in the world, watch this innings again but with a notebook and a pen. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/INDvENG?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#INDvENG</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/VjKQcdWzmj\">pic.twitter.com/VjKQcdWzmj</a></p>\n<p>— Wasim Jaffer (@WasimJaffer14) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WasimJaffer14/status/1371844690694258688?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 16, 2021</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p><div class=\'code-block code-block-27 ai-viewport-2 ai-viewport-3\' style=\'margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\'>\n<!-- Ezoic - long_content 106 - long_content -->\n<div id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-106\">\n<amp-ad width=\"100vw\" height=\"320\"\n     type=\"adsense\"\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-7948857487193175\"\n     data-ad-slot=\"5466720927\"\n     data-auto-format=\"rspv\"\n     data-full-width=\"\">\n  <div overflow=\"\"></div>\n</amp-ad>\n</div>\n<!-- End Ezoic - long_content 106 - long_content --></div>\n\n<p>Expecting Kohli to score a century tonight was unfair especially after considering the position India were in. However, this match will be added to the list of matches in which Kohli hasn&#8217;t scored a century since last scoring one in November 2019.</p>\n<p>It is worth mentioning that Kohli&#8217;s last international century had come against Bangladesh in India&#8217;s inaugural pink-ball Test match at the Eden Gardens. As far as Kohli&#8217;s last ODI century is concerned, it had come against West Indies during India&#8217;s tour of West Indies in 2019 at the Queen&#8217;s Park Oval.</p>\n<p>Since scoring his last international century, Kohli&#8217;s 1,436 runs in 39 innings across formats have come at an average of 42.23 including 14 half-centuries and a best of 94*.</p>\n<div class=\'code-block code-block-21 ai-viewport-2 ai-viewport-3\' style=\'margin: 8p