axheight=\"190\">\r\n                    <div class=\"\">\r\n                        <!-- Story Text -->\r\n                                <b class=\"place_cont\">\r\n                                    \r\n                                </b>\r\n</p><p><p>Rajasthan Royals (RR) aced the game on the field and social media on Saturday when they followed a <a href=\"https://sports.ndtv.com/ipl-2021/rr-vs-kkr-indian-premier-league-chris-morris-four-wicket-haul-helps-rajasthan-royals-seal-6-wicket-win-vs-kolkata-knight-riders-2421239\" target=\"_self\">comprehensive win over Kolkata Knight Riders</a> (KKR) in Mumbai with a social media post teasing KKR with a Shah Rukh Khan pose and a song from one of Shah Rukh\'s iconic films. RR posted on social media a short video where one of their players is seen recreating a popular Shah Rukh Khan move with song from the film <em>Dilwale Dulhaniya Le Jayenge</em> playing in the background.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><div id=\'checked\' style=\'display: none\' ><div id = \'adslotNativeVideo\' style = \'\' ><script>googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'adslotNativeVideo\');});</script></div></div></p><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"lt\">M.O.O.D. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HallaBol?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HallaBol</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RoyalsFamily?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#RoyalsFamily</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RRvKKR?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#RRvKKR</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/e4nu3ReC4K\">pic.twitter.com/e4nu3ReC4K</a></p>\r\n— Rajasthan Royals (@rajasthanroyals) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rajasthanroyals/status/1386018174361948162?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 24, 2021</a></blockquote><p><a href=\"https://sports.ndtv.com/ipl-2021/rr-vs-kkr-indian-premier-league-riyan-parags-selfie-celebration-with-tewatia-takes-twitter-by-storm-2421198\" target=\"_self\">RR dominated the contest</a> with both bat and ball as Chris Morris took 4 for 33 to restrict KKR to 133 for 9 in 20 overs.</p><p>The batsmen, led by captain Sanju Samson, didn\'t have any difficulty chasing the modest total at Wankhede Stadium as RR won by six wickets in 18.5 overs.</p><p></p><p>With this win Rajasthan moved off the bottom of the <a href=\"https://sports.ndtv.com/ipl-2021/indian-premier-league-2021-fans-respond-after-adam-gilchrist-asks-ipl-inappropriate-or-important-distraction-amid-covid-19-surge-2421139\" target=\"_self\">IPL 2021</a> points table and they are now placed sixth with four points from five matches.</p><p>KKR, on the other hand, have slipped to the bottom of the table with just two points from five games.<br />\r\nRR will now have a short break from cricket as they move from Mumbai to Delhi and take on Mumbai Indians in their next match on Thursday, April 29.</p><p class=\"mb-0\" style=\"width: 320px;margin: 0 auto;text-align: left;\"><span class=\"add_JIO-top-txt t-center\">Promoted</span><div id=\"jiosaavn-widget\"><div style=\"position:fixed;top:100%;\">Listen to the <a href=\"https://www.jiosaavn.com/featured/Nach_Le/UQjTO6rFZfc_\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">latest songs</a>, only on <a href=\"https://www.jiosaavn.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">JioSaavn.com</a></div></div><script defer>_rrCode.push(function() {(function(d, t) {var s = d.createElement(t);var s1 = d.createElement(t);if (d.getElementById(\'jsw-init\')) return;s.setAttribute(\'id\', \'jsw-init\');s.setAttribute(\'src\', \'https://www.jiosaavn.com/embed/_s/embed.js?ver=\' + Date.now());s.onload = function() { s1.appendChild(d.createTextNode(\'JioSaavnEmbedWidget.init({a:\"1\", q:\"1\", embed_src:\"https://www.jiosaavn.com/embed/playlist/5148894\",dfp_medium :\"1\",partner_id:\"ndtv\"});\')); d.body.appendChild(s1); };if (document.readyState === \'complete\'){d.body.appendChild(s);}else if (document.readyState === \'loading\'){var interval = setInterval(function() {if (document.readyState === \'complete\'){d.body.appendChild