"Web Stories,9\" href=\"/web-stories\" onclick=\"ga(\'send\', \'event\', \'ht_site\',\'subnav_click\', \'Web Stories\');\">Web Stories</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</aside> <section class=\"mainContainer\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n<a href=\"/\">Home</a>\n/ <a href=\"/cricket\">Cricket</a>\n/ \'He likes to be main man in teams, he isn\'t that here\': Pietersen on why he was \'skeptical\' about Maxwell\'s run at RCB\n</div>\n<div class=\"m_ads_unit\">\n<div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1524814893923-0\'>\n<script>\nif (isDeviceEnabled(\'small\') || isDeviceEnabled(\'medium\')) {\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function () { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1524814893923-0\'); });\n}\n</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"m_headBanner align-center\">\n<div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1611568220093-0\'>\n<script>\nif (isDeviceEnabled(\'small\') || isDeviceEnabled(\'medium\')) {\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1611568220093-0\'); });\n}\n</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"dataHolder\" data-title=\"Latest Cricket News Today, Live Cricket Score, Match Coverage, ICC Cricket News\" data-url=\"/cricket\" class=\"detailPage\" data-story-id=\"101619324926566\" data-story-section=\"cricket\" data-story-subsection=\"\">\n<div class=\"fullStory tfStory\" data-vars-storyid=\"101619324926566\">\n<figure class=\"\">\n<span>\n<img src=\"https://images.hindustantimes.com/img/2021/04/25/550x309/Pietersen_Maxwell_1619325172930_1619325186972.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Pietersen and Glenn Maxwell.(File/IPL)\" title=\"Kevin Pietersen and Glenn Maxwell.(File/IPL)\" />\n</span>\n<figcaption>Kevin Pietersen and Glenn Maxwell.(File/IPL)</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<div class=\"storyShortDetail liveBlogCart\">\n<div class=\"catName pt10\"><a href=\"/cricket\">cricket</a>\n</div>\n<h1 class=\"hdg1\">\'He likes to be main man in teams, he isn\'t that here\': Pietersen on why he was \'skeptical\' about Maxwell\'s run at RCB</h1>\n<div class=\"sortDec\">IPL 2021: But there is one person in the RCB squad - who deserves as much credit for the franchises\' success this year as Virat Kohli, Devdutt Padikkal. And even AB de Villiers. That person is Glenn Maxwell.</div>\n<div class=\"actionDiv\">\n<div class=\"socialEl\"><span class=\"bookmark bookmark-candidate\" title=\"bookmark\"></span><span class=\"share\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"readFull\">\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"dap-readmore\" data-articleid=\"101619324926566\">READ FULL STORY </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"stroyPub\">\n<div class=\"storyBy\">\nBy <a href=/author/hindustantimes-com-101607439170281>hindustantimes.com</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dateTime\">UPDATED ON APR 25, 2021 12:03 PM IST\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"storyDetails\">\n<div class=\"detail \">\n<p>Virat Kohli\'s Royal Challengers Bangalore have declared themselves to be the favourites to lift the Indian Premier League 2021 trophy this year after four straight wins in the tournament. The emphatic 10-wicket victory over Rajasthan Royals earlier this week, courtesy of a century from Devdutt Padikkal, has further shown how strong RCB\'s squad is in this season. (<a href=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/cricket/ipl\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>IPL 2021 Full Coverage</strong></a>)</p><p>But there is one person in the squad - who deserves as much credit for the franchise\'s success this year as Kohli, Padikkal. And even AB de Villiers. That person is Glenn Maxwell.</p><p><strong>Also read: </strong><a href=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/cricket/ipl-2021-rcb-predicted-xi-vs-csk-red-hot-royal-challengers-bangalore-likely-to-remain-unchanged-seek-fifth-straight-win-101619264307414.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>RCB Predicted XI vs CSK: Red-hot Royal Challengers Bangalore likely to remain unchanged, seek fifth win</strong></a></p><p>Maxwell, in the first four games, has smashed 176 runs at an average of 58.66 and a strike rate of 149.15 this season. But after last year\'s poor showing in the IPL, many were skeptical about RCB\'s purchase of the Aussie heavy-hitter, and one of them was former England batsman Kevin Pietersen.</p><p>\"I was sceptical of RCB’s purchase of Glenn Maxwell at the beginning of the tournament, partly because he is ‘The Big Show’ – he likes to be the main man in the teams he plays in,\" Pietersen wrote in a blog for Betway.</p><p>\"He certainly isn’t that here, with Virat Kohli and AB de Villiers at the top of the tree, so it’s surprised me that he’s done so well,\" Pietersen added.</p><p>\"He must feel very comfortable in the set-up there. I know that if you make Maxwell feel comfortable and pump his tyres a bit then you will see huge benefits,\" he further said.</p><p>\"He is a fabulous player. He can be inconsistent, but we haven’t seen that inconsistency yet this season,\" Pietersen signed off.</p><p>RCB will face off against Chennai Super Kings in the first game of IPL 2021\'s double-headers on Sunday.</p>\n<div class=\"shareArticle\">\n<span>SHARE THIS ARTICLE ON</span>\n<div class=\"shareIcons\">\n<a data-id=\"Share, 1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"ga(\'send\', \'event\', \'ht_site\',\'card_share_click\', \'share\'); window.open(\'whatsapp://send?text=\'He%20likes%20to%20be%20main%20man%20in%20teams%2C%20he%20isn\'t%20that%20here\'%3A%20Pietersen%20on%20why%20he%20was%20\'skeptical\'%20about%20Maxwell\'s%20run%20at%20RCB - https://www.hindustantimes.com/cricket/kevin-pietersen-explains-why-he-was-skeptical-about-rcb-purchase-of-glenn-maxwell-at-ipl-2021-auction-101619324926566.html?utm_source=whatsapp&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=ht_site\');\" class=\"wt\" title=\"what\'s app\" data-action=\"share/whatsapp/share\"></a>\n<a data-id=\"Share, 2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/cricket/kevin-pietersen-explains-why-he-was-skeptical-about-rcb-purchase-of-glenn-maxwell-at-ipl-2021-auction-101619324926566.html?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social&utm_camp